---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About" 
  description="Learn more about this blog and its author."
>
  <article class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">About This Blog</h1>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Hello, I'm Your Name</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Welcome to my personal blog! This is where I share my thoughts, experiences, 
          and insights about web development, technology, and life in general.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          I'm passionate about creating fast, accessible, and beautiful web experiences. 
          When I'm not coding, you can find me exploring new technologies, reading, 
          or enjoying the outdoors.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          This blog is built with modern web technologies including Astro, TypeScript, 
          and Tailwind CSS. It features full-text search powered by Pagefind and 
          comments powered by GitHub Discussions via Giscus.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a 
            href="https://github.com/yourname" 
            class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline transition-colors"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            GitHub
          </a>
          <a 
            href="https://twitter.com/yourname" 
            class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline transition-colors"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Twitter
          </a>
          <a 
            href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourname" 
            class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline transition-colors"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a 
            href="mailto:your.email@example.com" 
            class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline transition-colors"
          >
            Email
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="md:col-span-1">
        <div class="bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-zinc-700 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-4xl">
            üë®‚Äçüíª
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white text-center mb-2">Your Name</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 text-center text-sm mb-4">Web Developer & Blogger</p>
          <div class="text-center">
            <a 
              href="/blog" 
              class="inline-block bg-white text-zinc-900 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-zinc-200 transition-colors duration-200"
            >
              Read My Posts
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">What You'll Find Here</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">üöÄ Web Development</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 text-sm">
            Tutorials, tips, and insights about modern web development technologies 
            including React, Astro, TypeScript, and more.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">üí° Technology</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 text-sm">
            Thoughts on emerging technologies, tools, and trends that are shaping 
            the future of software development.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">üìö Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 text-sm">
            My journey of continuous learning, book recommendations, and resources 
            that have helped me grow as a developer.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">üéØ Personal</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 text-sm">
            Occasional personal reflections, productivity tips, and thoughts on 
            work-life balance in the tech industry.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">About This Site</h2>
      <div class="bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg p-6">
        <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          This blog is built with <strong>Astro</strong>, a modern static site generator 
          that delivers exceptional performance. The site features:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-zinc-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Content Collections</strong> with Zod schema validation for type-safe content</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Pagefind</strong> integration for fast, client-side search</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Giscus</strong> comments powered by GitHub Discussions</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> for modern, responsive styling</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>TypeScript</strong> for better developer experience</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>RSS feed</strong> and sitemap for SEO</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
          The source code is available on GitHub, and the site is deployed on Vercel 
          with automatic deployments from the main branch.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Get In Touch</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        I'd love to hear from you! Whether you have questions, suggestions, or just 
        want to say hello, feel free to reach out.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
        <a 
          href="/blog" 
          class="bg-white text-zinc-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-zinc-200 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          Read the Blog
        </a>
        <a 
          href="/rss.xml" 
          class="border border-zinc-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          Subscribe to RSS
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>